Torture: Belgium (CAT/C/CR/30/6). The Committee recommended that Belgium include &#8220;a 
provision in the Penal Code expressly prohibiting the invocation of a state of necessity to justify the 
violation of the right not to be subjected to torture&#8221; (para. 7 (b)). See also CAT/C/XXVII/Concl.5. 
</p>
