No. 213/1986, <i>H.C.M.A. v. The Netherlands</i>, 30 March 1989, para. 11.6; communication No. 
612/1995, <i>Vicente et al. v. Colombia</i>, 29 July 1997, para. 8.8; communication No. 1196/2003, 
